#. Tag: title
#: managingresources.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create resources for a project using the <link linkend=\"resource-"
"editor\">Resource Editor</link> and <link linkend=\"work-and-vacation-editor"
"\">Work and Vacation Editor</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vire za projekt lahko ustvarite z <link linkend=\"resource-editor"
"\">urejevalnikom virov</link> in <link linkend=\"work-and-vacation-editor"
"\">urejevalnikom dela in počitnic</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"However, if you are going to use the same resources in many projects (which "
"is often the case) it is more convenient to maintain resources in a separate "
"file. The best way to do this is to create your resources file first and "
"then set up &plan; to always load this file when creating a new project."
msgstr ""
"Če pa boste uporabljali iste vire v številnih projektih (kar se pogosto "
"zgodi), je bolj priročno vzdrževati vire v ločeni datoteki. Najboljši način "
"za to je, da najprej ustvarite svojo datoteko virov in nato nastavite &plan; "
"da to datoteko vedno naložite, ko ustvarjate nov projekt."

#. Tag: title
#: managingresources.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shared Resources"
msgstr "Viri v skupni rabi"

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shared Resources are resources that can be shared between project and thus "
"facilitates resource levelling across projects."
msgstr ""
"Viri v skupni rabi so viri, ki jih je mogoče deliti med projekti in tako "
"olajšajo izravnavo virov med projekti."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are managing projects that use totally different resource pools you "
"can create multiple resource files, but one project can only refer to one "
"resource file."
msgstr ""
"Če upravljate projekte, ki uporabljajo popolnoma različna področja virov, "
"lahko ustvarite več datotek virov, vendar se en projekt lahko nanaša samo na "
"eno datoteko virov."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the resource file to use when creating a new project. The "
"resources can be automatically loaded on opening your project or you can "
"update manually by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Update Shared Resources</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko datoteko virov, ki jo želite uporabiti pri ustvarjanju novega "
"projekta. Viri se lahko samodejno naložijo ob odpiranju vašega projekta ali "
"pa jih posodobite ročno tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Posodobi vire v skupni rabi</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that the project can still be opened even if the resource file is not "
"available."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je projekt še vedno mogoče odpreti, tudi če datoteka virov "
"ni na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If anything has been deleted in the shared resource file, you will be "
"presented with a dialog where you can select how to treat the deleted items."
msgstr ""
"Če je bilo karkoli izbrisano v datoteki virov v skupni rabi, se vam prikaže "
"pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko izberete, kako ravnati z izbrisanimi "
"elementi."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can select if an item shall be:"
msgstr "Izberete lahko, ali naj bo predmet:"

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Removed:</emphasis> Removes the item from your project. This is "
"the action you would normally select as it keeps your project in sync with "
"the resource file. However if the item is used in your project, you may want "
"to convert to a local item."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Odstranjen:</emphasis> Odstrani element iz vašega projekta. To je "
"dejanje, ki bi ga običajno izbrali, saj ohranja vaš projekt sinhroniziran z "
"datoteko virov. Če pa je element uporabljen v vašem projektu, ga boste morda "
"želeli pretvoriti v lokalni element."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>Converted:</emphasis> Converts the item to local item."
msgstr "<emphasis>Pretvorjen:</emphasis> Pretvori element v lokalni element."

#. Tag: para
#: managingresources.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Kept:</emphasis> Keeps the item as a shared item in your project. "
"Next time the resource file is loaded, you will be asked again how to treat "
"the item."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Ohranjen:</emphasis> Ohrani element kot element v skupni rabi v "
"vašem projektu. Naslednjič, ko se datoteka virov naloži, boste znova "
"vprašani, kako ravnati z elementom."
